{"word":"G2036 - ἔπω - épō - ep'-o - Answer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>épō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ep'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Answer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல், பேசு, கேள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to say, to speak, to tell, to call, to name, to ask, to command"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primary verb (used only in the definite past tense, the others being borrowed from <a href=\"#/G2046 - ἐρέω - eréō - er-eh'-o/2046\">G2046</a>, <a href=\"#/G4483 - ῥέω - rhéō - hreh'-o/4483\">G4483</a> and <a href=\"#/G5346 - φημί - phēmí - fay-mee'/5346\">G5346</a>); to <i>speak</i> or <i>say</i> (by word or writting): - answer, bid, bring word, call, command, grant, say (on), speak, tell. Compare <a href=\"#/G3004 - λέγω - légō - leg'-o/3004\">G3004</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}